{
  "stem": "26983.10",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- we were witnessing the whole annihilation of the Hungarian Jews, I told you, from April, when we were still in the Familienlager.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And later on, we could see all the transports till the late autumn from Hungaria.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But me-- from time to time, came other transports from Paris, I remember-- I remember once came to our block, to the Strafcommando, straight from Champs-Elysees.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A young father and a young boy about 11 or 12 came to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't know why and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jews.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we couldn't speak French.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was very strange.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From time to time, they came-- single people, for one reason or another.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, some other German, [NON-ENGLISH] they took from the gypsy camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But later on, block number nine and also 11-- when block 11 was a kind of little [INAUDIBLE] first aid, a laboratorium-- I mean, first aid when somebody broke or got something.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they had their own doctor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember he was from a Czech origin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And even I, myself, when I got something on my knee, and they had they best medication, of course, which they took from the parcels from the people who had been gassed.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they had the best things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave-- he gave me there, on this block number 11, the first aid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But these two blocks were also emptied, selection and so on, all the rest of the people went to live in the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And slowly, also the straf company was emptied.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the end-- But I want to ask you about the straf.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came, all kinds of people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our courtyard there was this famous--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our courtyard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It belonged to our block.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
